Lafarge May Increase Presence in Indian, Brazil, Les Echos Says

-- B y   F r a n c o i s   d e   B e a u p u y
-- 
2011-02-21T10:07:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-21/lafarge-may-increase-presence-in-indian-brazil-les-echos-says.html
  Lafarge SA  may add cement-making
capacity over time with acquisitions in countries such as Brazil
and  India  as the industry consolidates,  Les Echos  reported, in
an interview with Chief Executive Officer Bruno Lafont.  Partner  Anglo American Plc  won’t seek “in the very short
term” to exit a U.K. joint venture the companies said on Feb.
18 that they’re forming, the French business newspaper cited
Lafont as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Francois De Beaupuy in Paris at 
 fdebeaupuy@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
